**Item#:** SCP-7000-EX

**Object Class:** Explained (Formerely Keter/Chhokmah)

**Special Containment Procedures:** Director Pendant Roufhous is to be monitored while writing documentation for any and all future anomalies directed by them. Such documents are to then be reviewed extensively, prior to publishing and, by extension, enacting.

This document, alongside previous revisions of this document, are to be distributed to personnel in some way working alongside Director Pendant Roufhous, or personnel who request this document, provided they have Level-4 clearance.

The official SCP-7000 slot should preferably not be taken by another document, so as to highlight Director Roufhous' actions.

